# TOOLS.md

Which tools exist here and how to invoke them.

**MCP (primary):** Configure **one** URL: the Docker **MCP gateway** (`servers.gateway` ‚Üí `http://mcp-gateway:8811/mcp`). The plugin names that server **`gateway`**, so each flat tool id is **`gateway__`** + the aggregate MCP tool name (e.g. **`gateway__duckduckgo__search`**). **Never** stack another **`gateway__`** in front of that ‚Äî it is not a registered tool. This stack uses a forked `openclaw-mcp-bridge` that exposes **`gateway__call`** and **flat** tools matching whatever the gateway loads (e.g. **`gateway__tavily__tavily_search`**, **`gateway__comfyui__run_workflow`**). Use **`gateway__call`** with **`tool`** + **`args`**, or flat tools when listed. **Invalid** top-level names include **`gateway__run_workflow`** / **`comfyui__call`** ‚Äî see **TROUBLESHOOTING** if tools are missing.

**Do not guess ComfyUI inner names:** use **`list_workflows`** / **`comfyui__list_workflows`**, not `list_comfyui_workflows`. **Ports:** **`6680`** = OpenClaw gateway; **`11435`** = model-gateway **`/v1`**; **`11434`** = Ollama ‚Äî do not conflate them. Details: **`mcp/docs/openclaw-bridge-deep-dive.md`**.

**Search:** **`TAVILY_API_KEY`** in **`.env`** ‚Üí **Tavily** tools (**`tavily_search`**, **`tavily_extract`**, ‚Ä¶). Also **`gateway__duckduckgo__search`**. Do not use native **`web_search`**.

**Other MCP servers (catalog):** n8n, ComfyUI, etc. ‚Äî **`gateway__call`** with the live tool id and args, or flat **`gateway__‚Ä¶`** tools when present.

**Browser:** Built-in **`browser`** denied; no Playwright MCP by default. Use **Tavily** + **`web_fetch`**.

**ComfyUI:** Use **ComfyUI tools on the MCP gateway** (`list_workflows`, `run_workflow`, ‚Ä¶). Workflows are only under **`data/comfyui-storage/ComfyUI/user/default/workflows/`** (e.g. **`mcp-api/generate_image`**).

**Files and shell:** **`read`** / **`edit`** / **`exec`** per runtime for paths allowed in this workspace.

**Core services (inside the stack ‚Äî use hostnames, not `localhost`):**

| Service | Base |
|--------|------|
| Model Gateway | `http://model-gateway:11435/v1` |
| MCP Gateway | `http://mcp-gateway:8811/mcp` |
| Dashboard | `http://dashboard:8080` |
| Ollama | `http://ollama:11434` |
| ComfyUI | `http://comfyui:8188` |
| n8n | `http://n8n:5678` |
| OpenClaw UI | `http://openclaw-gateway:6680` |

**Discord:** **`message`** with **`to: "channel:<id>"`**, respect per-message size limits.

**Privileged stack ops:** **`DASHBOARD_AUTH_TOKEN`** + **`http://dashboard:8080`** API routes. See **mcp/docs/openclaw-hardening-and-operations.md**.

**Compose / host repairs:** **`agents/docker-ops.md`** (if present).
